14 land that is used for complementary ancillary commercial businesses other than senior care facilities and senior
15 housing, including but not limited to doctor's offices, rehabilitation facilities, grocery or convenience stores,
16 neighborhood restaurants, pharmacies, and workforce housing related to employment at senior care facilities.
