18 NEW SECTION. Section 7. Reports to local government by tax-exempt senior care and housing
19 sponsor. The board of a tax-exempt senior care and housing sponsor shall, at least once a year, file with the
20 governing body of the local government a report of its activities for the preceding year until the property tax
21 exemption in [section 6] expires.
22
23 NEW SECTION. Section 8. Rulemaking. The department may adopt rules to implement the
24 provisions of [sections 1 through 8].
